###Testing with Tap Water

To start with something easy, I took to tap water to test the filter.
The product had a chemical taste to me at first which didn't excite me.
After some research I found that this is [common for water straws.](http://lifestraw.com/faq/why-does-my-lifestraw-go-have-a-plastic-taste/)
I worked water through the filter until the taste had died down.

